# dotenvx-managed secrets for domeneshop-mcp (safe to commit once encrypted).
# Add the Domeneshop credential with:
#   pnpm dlx @dotenvx/dotenvx set DOMENESHOP_TOKEN  <token>
#   pnpm dlx @dotenvx/dotenvx set DOMENESHOP_SECRET <secret>
# That encrypts the values here and writes the decryption key to .env.keys
# (gitignored). Put that key in the lb-dev Key Vault as `domeneshop-mcp-dotenv-key`.
# Non-secret config (ENTRA_*, DOMAIN_ALLOWLIST, PORT, PUBLIC_URL) is set via the
# k8s deployment env, not here.
